sequenceDiagram
    actor Player
    participant System
    
    Note over Player, System: UC-05: Attack Enemy (Melee)
    Player->>System: clickEnemy(enemy)
    System-->>Player: showActionMenu(enemy)
    Player->>System: selectAction("ATTACK")
    
    System->>System: calculateDamage(Hero.STR, Weapon.ATK, Enemy.DEF)
    System->>System: reduceEnemyHP(damage)
    System->>System: deductHeroEnergy(attackCost)
    
    alt Enemy HP <= 0
        System->>System: remove Enemy from Map
        System->>System: roll for loot drop
    end
    
    System-->>Player: renderAttackAnimationAndUpdatedStats()